# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者賭博輸錢嘅時候，及時放棄，唔再繼續落注，避免損失擴大（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop loss
<eg>
yue:見到隻股票跌咗兩成，佢決定止蝕離場。 (gin3 dou2 zek3 gu2 piu3 dit3 zo2 loeng5 sing4, keoi5 kyut3 ding6 zi2 sit6 lei4 coeng4.)
eng:Seeing the stock had dropped 20%, he decided to cut his losses and exit. [end of text]


